Okey, Today I will tell you how to make a Server Control Pannel
[b]
What's a Server Control Pannel?[/b]
[i]Its a Control Pannel, what you can use, when your server is online, and when you want to say, to update, ..... something.[/i]

[b]Difficutly[/b]: 2/10
[b]Files what you need to use[/b]: CP.java (You will need to make this or you can Download it.), server.java


Here we go!

Okey, now you will have to download the CP.java file or you can just follow my steps.
But because this is the Download section I'll also put the Download link on it.

Download link: http://files.filefront.com/CPjava/;12200920;/fileinfo.html

After you have downloaded this, you only have the CP.java file, but you need to do some more steps.
Go to step 2 if you downloaded the file, otherways just follows those steps from in the beginning.

First you make a new notepad, and in the notepad you add all of this

